snippet.title: Dark Ace Saga Playthrough - Part 1 (Ace of Turnabouts - Day 1: Investigation)
snippet.description:
drvonkitty and I made Ace of Turnabouts and A Web of Turnabouts, and we're still in the process of making two more cases to complete this fangame. I'll be playing through each one with full commentary where I'll give some info on how these cases came to be.

drvonkitty's channel - https://youtube.com/@drvonkitty?si=kRCeeU78m5BhWfRp

Play the full game yourself here - https://aaonline.fr/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13023

Apologies for the audio quality. It's my first time making a video with my voice in it. It'll be better from the next video onwards.
